            },
            "description": "### Retrieve National Court House Details\n\nThis endpoint retrieves the details of a national court house based on the specified `id`.\n\n**HTTP Method:** GET  \n**Endpoint:** `{{baseURL}}/national-court-houses/{id}`\n\n#### Path Parameters\n\n- `id` (integer): The unique identifier of the national court house to retrieve.\n    \n\n#### Response\n\n- **Status Code:** 200 OK\n    \n- **Content-Type:** application/json\n    \n\n##### Response Body\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"id\": 0,\n  \"name\": \"\",\n  \"courtType\": \"\",\n  \"startDate\": \"\",\n  \"endDate\": null,\n  \"locationId\": 0,\n  \"psaId\": 0,\n  \"courtLocationCode\": \"\",\n  \"welshName\": \"\",\n  \"orgId\": 0\n}\n\n ```\n\nThis will return the details of the specified national court house, including its name, type, dates, and associated identifiers.\n\nThis endpoint retrieves information about national court houses.\n\n**HTTP Method:** GET  \n**URL:** `{{baseURL}}/national-court-houses?id=2`\n\n#### Request Parameters\n\n- **id** (required): The unique identifier for the national court house.\n    \n\n#### Response\n\n- **Status Code:** 400\n    \n- **Content-Type:** application/json\n    \n- **Response Body:**\n    \n    - `timestamp`: The timestamp of the error.\n        \n    - `status`: The status code of the error.\n        \n    - `error`: A description of the error.\n        \n    - `path`: The path of the request that caused the error.\n        \n\n**Note:** Ensure that the `id` parameter is provided to successfully retrieve the national court house information."
          },
          "response": []
        }
